Baseball Hall of Famers
The following elected members of the Baseball Hall of Fame played and/or managed for the Padres.
Gwynn, Winfield, Fingers, Gossage, Randy Jones, and Graig Nettles (3B, 1984&lt;U+2013&gt;1987) are also members of the San Diego Hall of Champions, which is open to athletes native to the San Diego area (such as Gwynn and Nettles) as well as to those who played for San Diego teams.
